WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.900
The package hub confirms readiness before opening the store.

00:08.900 --> 00:15.300
The customer browses the storefront catalog.

00:15.300 --> 00:25.200
A product is selected and reviewed in the cart.

00:25.200 --> 00:36.600
The synthetic checkout ends with a completed order.

00:36.600 --> 00:43.900
After the buying journey ends, the operator picks up the same order.

00:43.900 --> 00:53.300
The order is processed and reaches completed status.

00:53.300 --> 01:02.000
The connected result is visible without duplicate effects.
